{"tid":1393571,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"因病返日休養　Mina@TWICE由母親陪同抵韓","createTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T11:08:18.000Z","uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"422dbd332d8283cd57a15741aea7ef35dd87cee9","tid":1393571,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:40:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190801/photo/bkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_01p.jpg?20190801142503\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20190801142503&h=805fd186&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n在日本休息近一個月的Mina今午由母親陪同下返韓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190801/photo/bkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_02p.jpg?20190801142503\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_02p.jpg%3F20190801142503&h=d84178ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMina唇色蒼白，看起來十分虛弱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190801/photo/bkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190801142503\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190801142503&h=59641d89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n全程拖實媽媽。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190801/photo/bkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_04p.jpg?20190801142503\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_04p.jpg%3F20190801142503&h=687c2afe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMina的母親今日陪女兒返韓。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190801/photo/bkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_05p.jpg?20190801142503\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_05p.jpg%3F20190801142503&h=e9594fd9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMina疑似落淚。<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190801/photo/bkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_06p.jpg?20190801142503\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190801%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190801141337355-0801_00862_001_06p.jpg%3F20190801142503&h=b147e6f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n經理人代Mina收下鮮花。<br />\n<br />\n韓國人氣女團TWICE的22歲日本成員Mina上月5日因健康理由而缺席活動，其後所屬的JYP事務所指Mina因為突然對舞台感到極度緊張和不安，需要停工接受治療及靜養，不會參與TWICE接下來的世界巡唱，而回家鄉日本休息近一個月的Mina，今午與母親一起返韓。<br />\n<br />\nMina步出機場時拖實母親，並用漁夫帽遮面，見她唇色蒼白，全程用毛氈包住上身，看起來十分虛弱，身旁的經理人不時拍拍Mina的膊頭以示安慰，而Mina一度忍不住落淚，情緒似乎不太穩定，有粉絲向Mina遞上鮮花，由經理人代為收下。不少粉絲都留言送祝福，希望Mina早日康復。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4aacefda15afa1326d7228a06a3357ab532fc80b","tid":1393571,"uid":37146,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:44:37.000Z","msg":"早日康復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔抖耐啲......<br />\n屌你老母JYP"},{"pid":"b44c5057031031196e05fa40a2858102819bcf1c","tid":1393571,"uid":74065,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:50:57.000Z","msg":"如果養病應該唔洗返韓?<br />\n但又好多行李<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748feef22ac4d1d01f60a98b8aa949acea45fc5f","tid":1393571,"uid":62822,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T06:55:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3c24b4149e19d171b162dc26